{"tid":1543763,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"見到示威者拎武士刀斬警察，我真係好擔心","createTime":"2019-09-05T10:07:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T13:23:15.000Z","uid":41205,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"43bdab4e3005d482afc23ee906bd67570ea666c0","tid":1543763,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:07:18.000Z","msg":"到底宜家咩世界，執法人員要受到咁樣既對待？<br />\n<br />\n暴徒扮做普通市民，原來佢褲袋一早暗藏一把凶狠既武士刀<br />\n<br />\n你話我地英勇既警察哥哥又無做壞事，又唔係話打死人老強人輪姦人，比暴徒咁偷襲，天理何在？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b09d8430d1e01c37f32f12916a6535a5dc3b303","tid":1543763,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:07:25.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d14e54774a61ea7a832052ebcf92d385734fd4a2","tid":1543763,"uid":117082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:07:50.000Z","msg":"曲撚到"},{"pid":"95ba8ff992defa606517553356adc44b073e484e","tid":1543763