2019<br />\n梅先生（32歲） - 5/7/2019<br />\n范先生（26歲） - 22/7/2019<br />\nCalvin 郭先生（25歲） - 27/8/2019<br />\n姬先生（16歲） - 2/9/2019 <br />\n何小姐（27歲） - 4/9/2019<br />\n9人離世<br />\n<br />\n還有：<br />\n4隻眼<br />\n2次地鐵恐襲<br />\n2人被刀手斬至重傷<br />\n超過100人被檢控<br />\n超過1000人被捕<br />\n受傷, 逃亡不計其數<br />\n<br />\n淨係計以上的分別, 已經好明顯。<br />\n還有整個警隊及制度的不公義已暴露。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkC3deC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkC3deC.jpg&h=34367fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D2LPVhj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD2LPVhj.jpg&h=35c3dac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C4TBAhk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC4TBAhk.jpg&h=05bdd3d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8udugLx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8udugLx.jpg&h=bae3ed34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ZTBFS9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ZTBFS9.jpg&h=3e1d2264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=90f7b133\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a>"},{"pid":"8d3f327258858803866388b6ffc092a2352f00aa","tid":1543763,"uid":32485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:10:54.000Z","msg":"圓月彎刀呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8589280efedb1fd1fa1587b47c3c9402e11b546a","tid":1543763,"uid":310030,"like":3,"disl